title: The DDFP - Top 100 reaction podcast No. 70-61
itunes:title: The DDFP - Top 100 reaction podcast No. 70-61
description:
It is the first special edition of the Dave Dameshek Football  Program, as Dave’s critiques have driven him to offer you his instant opinion on the NFL’s Top 100 show on Sunday night on NFL Network. In this show, Dave and Adam Rank take a look at this week’s reveal, and talk about some of the biggest surprises of the week. To make a long story short, it’s a thin slice of heaven. 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
